Package: TCDT
Title: Two-Sample Conditional Distribution Testing 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhuoxi", "Li", , "lizhuoxi@ust.hk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jian", "Yan", , "jy929@cornell.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Xianyang", "Zhang", , "zhangxiany@stat.tamu.edu", role = "aut")
  )
Description: This package provides tools for performing two-sample tests to determine if two conditional distributions are the same. It implements the methods proposed by Yan, Li and Zhang (2025), using either conditional energy distance (CED) or conditional maximum mean discrepancy (CMMD).
